The paper is about DL compilers, which are tools used to optimize and deploy DL models on different hardware platforms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SE (Software Engineering) since DL compilers involve both ML and software engineering techniques. The paper also discusses the design of DL compilers, which could fall under cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.AR (Architecture).
